  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, I saw you watched the East Bengal Mohun Bagan match, what stood out for you in that comeback win?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The second half was amaaazing! East Bengal played so well after they scored the equalizer. I was so nervous but then the third goal came. What a game! Did you watch it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "The second half was amaaazing! East Bengal played so well after they scored the equalizer. I was so nervous but then the third goal came. What a game! Did you watch it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I did! The atmosphere at the field was out of this world. Everyone was shouting, and the players were so focused. Even though Mohun Bagan played good in the first half, East Bengal never gave up. That third goal was like magic!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That third goal was indeed magic! The players' focus and the crowd's energy made it unforgettable. East Bengal's never give up attitude is amazing to watch. What part of the match excited you most?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The third goal was the best part for me! The way they passed the ball and then the shot—it was so precise. I was on the edge of my seat! But the first goal of the second half also made me jump. You know, when they equalized? That was pure joy! Football is so exciting."
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Got it, the third goal’s precision and the equalizer’s joy stood out. Football moments like that are pure magic. What’s one game you’ll never forget?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The Kolkata Derby between East Bengal and Mohun Bagan on May 20, 2023, was like no other—so intense, so emotional. I was watching it with my friends, and when East Bengal scored that late winner, we all went mental! It was like *phele* (in Bengali) we were crying, then we were shouting. Unforgettable!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds incredible! Watching with friends and feeling all those emotions together must have made it even more special. What was the best part of that moment for you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The best part was when the final whistle blew and we all jumped up shouting *hooray!*! I felt so proud of East Bengal, and my friends were hugging each other like mad. The way the game turned around in the last 10 minutes? Just crazy! It was one of those moments you carry with you forever."
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds like a moment of pure joy and pride! Carrying it with you forever makes it extra special. What games are you excited for now?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The next big game I’m waiting for is the ISL final! I don’t know which team will win, but I hope it’s as crazy as the derby. Also, I’m keeping an eye on some international matches—maybe Brazil vs. Argentina next month? Not sure, but football always brings hope and excitement!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "The ISL final and Brazil vs. Argentina sound exciting! Hope brings the best energy to football. What makes a match \"crazy\" for you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "A \"crazy\" match is when anything can happen—goals in the last minute, red cards, comebacks from nowhere. The Kolkata Derby was crazy because it had all that! And when the crowd is going wild, you just feel the energy. It’s not just a game anymore—it’s like a storm! I think that’s what I love most about football."
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Got it, when the crowd and the game turn into a storm of energy, that’s football at its best. What’s a match you’re hoping becomes a storm soon?"
    }
  ],
